results.title: Grimm
results.Synopsis: A homicide detective discovers he is a descendant of hunters who fight supernatural forces.

results.title: Game of Thrones
results.Synopsis: Nine noble families fight for control over the mythical lands of Westeros, while an ancient enemy returns after being dormant for thousands of years.

results.title: Arrow
results.Synopsis: Spoiled billionaire playboy Oliver Queen is missing and presumed dead when his yacht is lost at sea. He returns five years later a changed man, determined to clean up the city as a hooded vigilante armed with a bow.
results.Category: Action | Adventure | Crime | Drama | Mystery | Sci-Fi

results.title: The Walking Dead
results.Synopsis: Sheriff Deputy Rick Grimes wakes up from a coma to learn the world is in ruins, and must lead a group of survivors to stay alive.

results.title: Dark Matter
results.Synopsis: In the dystopian 27th century, six people wake up on a deserted spaceship with no memory of who they are or what they're doing there. They reluctantly team up and set off to find answers with the help of a female android.

results.title: Vikings
results.Synopsis: Vikings transports us to the brutal and mysterious world of Ragnar Lothbrok, a Viking warrior and farmer who yearns to explore - and raid - the distant shores across the ocean.
results.Category: Action | Adventure | Drama | History | Romance | War

results.title: Peaky Blinders
results.Synopsis: A gangster family epic set in 1919 Birmingham, England; centered on a gang who sew razor blades in the peaks of their caps, and their fierce boss Tommy Shelby.

results.title: Black Sails
results.Synopsis: Follows Captain Flint and his pirates twenty years prior to Robert Louis Stevenson's classic novel Treasure Island.

results.title: Spartacus
results.Synopsis: The life of Spartacus, the gladiator who lead a rebellion against the Romans. From his time as an ally of the Romans, to his betrayal and becoming a gladiator, to the rebellion he leads and its ultimate outcome.
results.Category: Action | Adventure | Biography | Drama | History | Romance

results.title: Killjoys
results.Synopsis: In the Quad, a planetary system on the brink of a bloody interplanetary class war, a fun loving trio of bounty hunters attempt to remain impartial as they chase deadly warrants.

results.title: The Expanse
results.Synopsis: A police detective in the asteroid belt, the first officer of an interplanetary ice freighter and an earth-bound United Nations executive slowly discover a vast conspiracy that threatens the Earth's rebellious colony on the asteroid belt.

results.title: Westworld
results.Synopsis: Set at the intersection of the near future and the reimagined past, explore a world in which every human appetite can be indulged without consequence.

results.title: Breaking Bad
results.Synopsis: A high school chemistry teacher diagnosed with inoperable lung cancer turns to manufacturing and selling methamphetamine in order to secure his family's future.

results.title: Black Mirror
results.Synopsis: An anthology series exploring a twisted, high-tech world where humanity's greatest innovations and darkest instincts collide.

results.title: Rick and Morty
results.Synopsis: An animated series that follows the exploits of a super scientist and his not-so-bright grandson.

results.title: Da Vinci's Demons
results.Synopsis: Follows Leonardo Da Vinci during his early days in Florence, as a young artist, inventor and dreamer, trying to change the future.
results.Category: Adventure | Biography | Drama | Fantasy | History | Mystery | Romance

results.title: Sanctuary
results.Synopsis: Stem cells, gene therapy, transplants, and cloning have changed the definition of humanity in the modern world, but the darker side contains monsters that only few are brave enough to face, because the future lies in their hands.

results.title: Stargate: Atlantis
results.Synopsis: An international team of scientists and military personnel discover a Stargate network in the Pegasus Galaxy and come face-to-face with a new, powerful enemy, The Wraith.

results.title: Sherlock
results.Synopsis: A modern update finds the famous sleuth and his doctor partner solving crime in 21st century London.

results.title: Friends
results.Synopsis: Follows the personal and professional lives of six twenty to thirty-something-year-old friends living in Manhattan.
